sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client / Dashboard
    participant EvalHub as EvalHub API<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant MLflow as MLflow Server<br/>5000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant AdapterJob as Adapter Job Pod
    participant ModelEP as Model Inference<br/>Endpoint HTTPS
    participant S3 as AWS S3<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: Evaluation Job Creation and Execution

    Client->>EvalHub: POST /api/v1/evaluations/jobs<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (K8s TokenReview)
    EvalHub->>K8sAPI: TokenReview + SAR validation<br/>Auth: SA Token
    K8sAPI-->>EvalHub: Auth confirmed

    EvalHub->>MLflow: Create experiment / run<br/>Auth: Projected SA Token
    MLflow-->>EvalHub: Experiment ID

    EvalHub->>K8sAPI: Create ConfigMap<br/>(job configuration)<br/>Auth: SA Token
    K8sAPI-->>EvalHub: ConfigMap created

    EvalHub->>K8sAPI: Create batch/v1 Job<br/>(adapter container)<br/>Auth: SA Token
    K8sAPI-->>EvalHub: Job created

    EvalHub-->>Client: 201 Created (Job ID)

    Note over AdapterJob,S3: Flow 2: Test Data Initialization

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note right of AdapterJob: Init Container Phase
        AdapterJob->>S3: Download test data<br/>Auth: AWS credentials (secret mount)
        S3-->>AdapterJob: Test datasets
    end

    Note over AdapterJob,ModelEP: Adapter Job Execution

    AdapterJob->>ModelEP: Inference requests<br/>Auth: API Key / Token (secret)
    ModelEP-->>AdapterJob: Model responses

    AdapterJob->>EvalHub: POST /api/v1/evaluations/jobs/{id}/events<br/>Auth: Bearer Token<br/>(status callback)
    EvalHub-->>AdapterJob: 200 OK

    AdapterJob->>MLflow: Log results<br/>Auth: Projected SA Token
    MLflow-->>AdapterJob: Results stored

    Note over Client,EvalHub: Status Polling

    Client->>EvalHub: GET /api/v1/evaluations/jobs/{id}<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    EvalHub-->>Client: Job status + results
